headline: 2 Reasons to Like LII and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, Lennox’s stock price fell to $539.64. Shareholders have lost 8% of their capital, which is disappointing considering the S&P 500 has climbed by 15.6%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
